N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 91.11 - Where to submit registrations, annual filings and other submissions

State Regulations

Charitable organizations must submit their annual filing to the New York City

Office of the Attorney General's Charities Bureau, Registration Section, 28 Liberty Street, New York, NY 10005, or such other place as the Attorney

General may designate or electronically in the manner prescribed by statute or by the Attorney General. Notes
